{"tid":454800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國強回應明年初離任傳聞：你係咪好想我快啲走？","createTime":"2017-11-01T13:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T01:43:06.000Z","uid":8171,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"77697dce1c23ec82d7737eaf7332d50fdb7dec1d","tid":454800,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"網媒《眾新聞》日前引述不具名消息指，律政司長袁國強最快或在明年初離任。袁國強今日出席立法會會議後，未有正面回應報道，稱不會討論此問題，又向記者笑言「你係咪好想我快啲走？」<br />\n<br />\n問及會否完成高鐵一地兩檢工作後便離任，袁國強稱：「大家不如關心一地兩檢個問題會好啲。」他未有回應有否信心政府提出的高鐵一地兩檢無約束力議案，能在明日通過。"},{"pid":"09c62cee290445261621e9be8e5aad1b5100b86c","tid":454800,"uid":8171,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"係就快，唔好等下禮拜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b2041447936cc6115e8e51256bd9af823a1ce6","tid":454800,"uid":102562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c953d55e7437e071981f6b45fdb2b75177b7b8b","tid":454800,"uid":44358,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"想你快啲生cancer啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ceb5f3d9ee0d11c8d3cdfa85e9be2c2b3ede4c","tid":454800,"uid":67325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"係呀"},{"pid":"fda7d4cce86fd161a8aaf84de66691758cf08318","tid":454800,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:33:48.000Z","msg":"係! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed203a6a164dd636ec2f3d0bde7d019d14a13bb2","tid":454800,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"強國猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c4e1e032929adba3983a7728bf570114f94d9a","tid":454800,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike